txt.en: When the Taurogrim attacked the Beornings, the supplies from their cart were scattered all over the forest. Help the Beornings gather the lost items so they can return to their home.
Sterkist can be found at The Forest Gate, on the western edge of Eryn Lasgalen.\n\nYou should talk to Sterkist.
Sterkist checks a list from his cart and nods approvingly.\n\n'This seems to be everything that was missing! Thank you, [placeholder]'
The Beornings' supplies are scattered in Eryn Lasgalen.\n\nYou should gather the lost supplies.

'When we were first ambushed by the Taurogrim, our horse was spooked and our cart was overturned. The horse and cart are both fine, but many of our supplies are missing. I suspect the Taurogrim have taken some of them. While you are helping Thorlind deal with these wood-trolls, would you keep an eye out for anything we may have lost? Meet us at The Forest Gate once you have gathered them.'
